### Assign Default Shift to All Employees
### This file contains HTTP requests to assign shifts using the existing API

### 1. First, let's try to get available shifts
GET http://localhost:5099/api/shifts
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get all employees
GET http://localhost:5099/api/employees
Accept: application/json

### 3. Create shift assignments for all employees
### (You'll need to modify this based on the actual API structure)
POST http://localhost:5099/api/shift-assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shiftId": 1,
  "assignmentType": "Employee",
  "employeeId": 1,
  "effectiveDate": "2025-09-17",
  "status": "Active",
